reviewText: My son loves this show and I must say that I find it pretty amusing as well.
A good fun series. Great enjoyment for the whole family
Great new series love the cgi animation clever story's very enjoyable for young and old alike . Highly recommend great family entertainment

My 4 year old loves Super Hero Squad (I do too, don't tell)

The Superhero Squad continues its hilarious assault on the Marvel universe with antics ranging from the antics of She-Hulk, Hercules, too many Wolverines and Firestar (the canon immigrant from "Spider-Man & His Amazing Friends"). For more hilarity than you can shake a stick at, look no further.
